{
  "stem": "15576.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People saw-- a few of our people saw upstairs what's going on, and they brought to that people, old friends of ours, also [INAUDIBLE] threw them on the exit, supposedly.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not people that were with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you couldn't move this, because they would know for sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So on the side, at the same exit, there was a hall that we would creep out through the ground.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we made another secret exit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these people remained there till the liberation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they got a decent burial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was already-- I was there, and I knew the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Russians came in-- the Germans came in, and then the Russians beat them back, and we didn't know who was outside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then at worst, we went to scout.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had my things mixed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day I'm sitting, and I hear the shooting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, you know, it was like the air sucked in mother house outside-- you couldn't talk about anything, but you could hear everything outside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm sitting there, and I wonder if the sun is out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I hear a Russian outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm climbing out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I climbed out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took a look at myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started going towards Korolowka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was around 5 o'clock at night already or 6 o'clock, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was dark already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I hear [NON-ENGLISH], who's there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just started hollering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Please don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And two Russian soldiers, they're drunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One goes to the other and says, why don't we kill this kid?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What does he have to suffer for?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I heard this, I was-- I got prepped to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then starts another episode after the grotto.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
